column4: Qualcomm shows off wireless charging for electric vehicles
column5: SAN FRANCISCO Qualcomm Inc said on Thursday it had demonstrated how electric vehicles could be charged wirelessly while driving  a technology some believe will help accelerate the adoption of self-driving cars.

column4: Cisco revenue forecast disappoints; says to cut 1 100 more jobs
column5: Cisco Systems Inc  forecast current-quarter revenue that widely missed analysts' estimates and said it would cut 1 100 more jobs  as the world's largest networking gear maker steps up efforts to transform into a software-focused company.
